returning for a midnight ride.

00:00:56.180 --> 00:01:01.949
Other attractions include limited ward skins,
exclusive summoner icons and the mystery gift

00:01:01.949 --> 00:01:02.949
feature.

00:01:02.949 --> 00:01:05.920
Which allows you to purchase a random skin
for a friend.

00:01:05.920 --> 00:01:10.610
The mystery gift will only set you back 490
Rp and could end up being an ultimate skin

00:01:10.610 --> 00:01:11.610
worth three thousand.

00:01:11.610 --> 00:01:16.010
A word of warning to anyone thinking of buying
a mystery gift, make sure you write down which

00:01:16.010 --> 00:01:20.950
skin the gift ended up being because once
you close the dialog window there is NO way

00:01:20.950 --> 00:01:25.780
