champions 1 skin at a time.

00:01:25.780 --> 00:01:28.380
Nasus is next in line for a visual update.

00:01:28.380 --> 00:01:32.270
And judging from the preliminary screenshots
released last thursday things were looking

00:01:32.270 --> 00:01:33.270
good.

00:01:33.270 --> 00:01:37.140
But when the sound of Nasus's new voice and
sight of his new splash art hit the PBE.

00:01:37.140 --> 00:01:39.810
The league community was anything but pleased.

00:01:39.810 --> 00:01:45.090
For those who weren't aware Nasus was originally
voiced by singer / songwriter Gene Mcdaniels

00:01:45.090 --> 00:01:47.270
who passed away in 2011 at the age of 76.

00:01:47.270 --> 00:01:53.159
So the thought of Gene being immortalized
as the voice of Nasus was a romantic notion,

00:01:53.159 --> 00:01:58.399
but riot ultimately decided to update the
original voice over saying that QUOTE "The

00:01:58.399 --> 00:02:03.479
