has expanded significantly since Nasus originally

00:02:03.479 --> 00:02:08.009
made his debut, But during the process of
updating Nasus we've done everything possible

00:02:08.009 --> 00:02:11.400
to preserve the spirit of the original voiceover."

00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:16.350
But his new splash art seemed to tell a different
story, portraying him as a snarling and ferocious

00:02:16.350 --> 00:02:20.620
beast instead of the stoic and noble curator
we all know and love.

00:02:20.620 --> 00:02:24.890
