00:02:51.390 --> 00:02:55.280
Let's talk about season 4, I mean I don't
really want to because I'm still trying to

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:59.530
reach my goal for season 3, but none the less
there are some pretty excellent changes coming

00:02:59.530 --> 00:03:00.900
down the pipe.

00:03:00.900 --> 00:03:05.200
And the most excellent of those changes being
that player health bars and allied health

00:03:05.200 --> 00:03:09.870
bars now have a color distinction, so keeping
track of where you are in a team fight should

00:03:09.870 --> 00:03:11.720
be that much easier.

00:03:11.720 --> 00:03:15.530
Masteries have also been reworked and while
nothing is final cool changes include the

00:03:15.530 --> 00:03:20.160
addition of a spawn shield in the defence
tree, as well as the ability to generate three

00:03:20.160 --> 00:03:24.140
gold every time you hit an enemy champion
hit in the utility tree.

00:03:24.140 --> 00:03:29.240
Next a ranked and unranked 1v1 and 2v2 mode
has been added to the PBE and while you could

00:03:29.240 --> 00:03:35.150
assume that means the Magma chamber debuted
in June is implemented the entire doesn't

00:03:35.150 --> 00:03:36.590
seem to work at all right now.

00:03:36.590 --> 00:03:43.900
And last on my list of cool changes for season
4 is the new jungle camp... the wight camp.

00:03:43.900 --> 00:03:47.570
Originally intended to give single target
junglers like master yi and warwick a quick

00:03:47.570 --> 00:03:52.890
kill it succeeds only in making the average
jungle clear time longer... not to mention

00:03:52.890 --> 00:03:55.210
the uninspired aesthetic design of the mob.

00:03:55.210 --> 00:04:00.810
